board

Class Tile

  • java.lang.Object
    • board.Tile

  • public class Tile
extends java.lang.Object
    Tile class represents a single piece in the board. Holds 2 type of data: - States (int value to show state of the tile). - Objects (Any object).
    Version:
    2.0
    Author:
    Selcuk Gulcan
